{"type": "article", "id": 61995, "title": "给手机装一个“法拉第笼”，希望改善你的“手机上瘾症”｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-12T23:13:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57221, "name": "Atelier JM"}, {"id": 57222, "name": "Sozen"}, {"id": 26110, "name": "Stellar Works"}, {"id": 47567, "name": "Space Copenhagen"}, {"id": 52289, "name": "Crème"}, {"id": 57223, "name": "Mario Alessiani"}, {"id": 57224, "name": "章俊杰"}, {"id": 57225, "name": "Ernst Koning"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190312203531WzCBJqMf0Q5PcrjR.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><h3>Block by Ernst Koning </h3><p>阿姆斯特丹产品设计师 Ernst Koning 设计了一种便携式六角形法拉第笼（ Faraday cage ），目的是帮助我们摆脱智能手机的束缚。</p><p>Block 其实是一个网状包裹的防电磁屏蔽铝制外壳，可以存储多达七个智能手机，阻止它们的所有连接。</p><p>最初的法拉第笼由英国科学家 Michael Faraday 于 1836 年发明。与 Michael Faraday 的发明一样，Block 使用其铝皮来消散外部或内部电磁场产生的任何电流，包括 wifi 和其他电话信号。</p><p>“只需将手机放入其中并关闭盖子，就能阻挡所有传入和传出的信号。” Ernst Koning 说，他认为离线已成为一种奢侈品。“Block 让人们与智能手机建立更健康的关系，并有机会与家人和朋友重新联系。”</p><p>Block 声称其六角形外壳采用黄色、黑色或绿色铝制，比简单地关闭手机更有效，因为它将设备从用户的视线中移除。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203603RjNiD0BYngoaLbJc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203603Of8qFZpRVl5xAmva.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203604FhP1QAnLrG7tRl32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.173012\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203620NqXirxa7c4zhCb5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/03/12/block-phone-faraday-cage/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Slow collection of furniture by Stellar Works</h3><p>设计上海已于上周六告一段落，设计品牌 Stellar Works 携 Slow 系列新品首次亮相。</p><p>由丹麦设计双人组 Space Copenhagen 操刀设计的 Slow 系列，于 2017 年首度推出后广受好评，2019 年更加延伸系列产品，在设计上海首次亮相，包含五层开放式书架、双人椅及咖啡桌等，以浅色胡桃木搭配同色系牛皮。</p><p>纽约设计团队 Crème 与 Stellar Works 将经典温莎椅重新诠释，共同打造 Exchange 系列，推出摇椅版本新单品。Wohlert 系列单品，以 Louisiana 椅为首，最初于 1958 年由丹麦代表性设计师 Vilhelm Wohlert 为了路易斯安那现代艺术博物馆而设计，并于博物馆成立 60 周年之际，由 Stellar Works 再现经典单品。</p><p>此外，Stellar Works 还带来限量惊喜给经典家具爱好者，Risom 系列单品全球限量 20 套，此次展出全套 7 件单品皆选用高光亮漆，再现 1950、60 年代家具风潮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203651A6ejaMzDG1RHXpgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203651iSIaRVWCkhnq3FXB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665821\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903122036519zSMikrZAcKa7BXq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203652i6SZzb9yAjaRLntE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203735nXkZzjbWUBm3IFTN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Bamboo Softness lighting collection by Sozen</h3><p>由中国美术学院老师章俊杰创立的设计品牌素生，在最近的设计上海展会期间，推出竹编灯罩系列新品灯具。</p><p>整个系列采用弯曲的竹子布置，形成有机的空心形状，可用作灯罩。相交的平行线组成的波浪图案，当光线投射穿过它们时形成错综复杂的阴影。</p><p>在设计师多年的实验中，他惊奇地发现竹子具有弹性。他决定通过创造一系列编织产品来进一步探索这一点。Bamboo Softness 项目旨在测试竹子弹性的极限并显示其柔软的特性。“竹子非常结实，坚韧，但也有柔软的一面。”他说。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203801UaZM2YBXFAe8lNDJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203801x6F9u501jGYLDtWA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203801NoJ1OMErAuUvtBa3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019031220380159KpYmQjrcS7gL1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.114213\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203802O24w8hARNEy5Ppek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203802PHvGmojRLeDiSxcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.348562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203802Oj04rSE1iKNRDysz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/03/12/jun-jie-zhang-bamboo-softness-lighting/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Tongue by Mario Alessiani</h3><p>意大利产品设计师 Mario Alessiani 设计了一个模块化的瓶架，来展示葡萄酒系列。这个系列名为 Tongue，壁挂式设计类似于卷曲的舌头。</p><p>设计师将钢板折叠起来以形成单个葡萄酒瓶的支撑点。可以垂直、水平或随机排列多个组件以容纳更多酒瓶。目前，Tongue 提供灰煤色和红酒色两种款式，售价 49 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.hiro.design/it/compra/78-246-tongue-portabottiglie.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203844kWuICpzf05jiT9UN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203844jwWeZxT3orfHG7VC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203845wTEX5zVR1Ugv9cSm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203844cqD4hNGVfywW1Y0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203845iYy89xZRSmz51Qet.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203845M5PxX3Nr8Aj2nGQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-modular-tongue-inspired-wine-bottle-holder-by-mario-alessiani/tongue-wine-mario-alessiani-2a/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Eclipse Mirror lamp by Atelier JM</h3><p>在上个月的斯德哥尔摩家具和照明展会上，Atelier JM 设计工作室推出了一款名为 Eclipse 的壁挂式镜灯，可调节的结构意在模仿日蚀现象。</p><p>Eclipse 通过滑动可调节照明组件来表现出反射和透明的混合现象，设计团队的目标是在灯转换时通过人工照明唤起自然日光的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203919gmCK75NjbkPxXqfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019031220391974r9pj1gL6cKOvmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203919aXunLWBjlPE6OQ2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203920VzgeZYQJBpTlxs2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203920JrHoYAk97D3tMeQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203920mlUTihsqRejbo0xH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203920IyHUjma61NGfLi9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190312203920JR4sQGuipnV8MI0m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.595313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}